txt.en: 'You're late maggot! We already have a hold on this city. Soon those foolish men will run away or die by my sword!\n\n'What?! You're still standing here. Go get some order from the other war-leaders or I'll send you on a mission to your death! Har, har!'
Listen to Khúrhosh give you orders
Grazadhal doesn't like that you showed up late and orders you to traverse the city to assist captains in their reach for favour from the Dark Lord.
'Those pesky men are just on the other side of the river! I've held this post by myself before and I'll do it again if I have to!\n\n'If you want to stick around, better make yourself useful!'
Listen to Dulglok give you orders
'What's this?! Another measly recruit?! Bah, I don't have time for you.\n\n'Better make yourself useful or I'll deal with you myself!'
Listen to Shíktarb give you orders
Orc captains can be found in the main strongholds of the Morgul army.\n\nYou should speak with the other Orc captains of the Morgul army.
'Of course I'm Shíktarb. Do you see anyone else of importance around here?\n\n'You want to work for me and kill those rotten men, I'll work you to the bone!'
